How tall is P.J. Tucker?

P.J. Tucker is 6-5 (196 cm) tall.

How much does P.J. Tucker weigh?

P.J. Tucker weighs 245 lbs (111 kg).

Is P.J. Tucker in the Hall of Fame?

P.J. Tucker is not in the Hall of Fame.

Small Forward, Power Forward, and Shooting Guard.

P.J. Tucker has won one championship.
